{"tid":164844,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"家中 20 萬美元珠寶首飾被闖門偷光 Kendall Jenner 氣到炒了所有保鑣！","createTime":"2017-03-21T03:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T06:41:15.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0715e1f68fc0b84038b540b03cff8756c952f9c5","tid":164844,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63815/58cda75f6a680.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63815%2F58cda75f6a680.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=766e1a23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國名媛卡戴珊家族似乎已經成為珠寶盜賊的目標，繼金卡戴珊（Kim Kardashian）在巴黎發生了轟動的持槍搶案之後，21 歲新生代超模坎達兒&middot;珍娜（Kendall Jenner）最新爆出她位於好萊塢山丘的豪宅內，被偷走了價值 20 萬美元、約 610 萬台幣的珠寶飾品，讓她氣到炒了當時在場的整個保鑣團隊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63815/58cda75e87e21.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63815%2F58cda75e87e21.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=e8a009f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在這周三晚間，坎達兒&middot;珍娜約了數名朋友來百萬裝潢又一村月中閣1,433呎家裡開派對，在他們於樓下設計以暖色簡約為主，黃色牆身，配合淺褐色地板，營造舒適溫馨的家居開趴的期間，坎達兒&middot;珍娜曾經聽到家裡的警報鈴聲響起，當時她不以為意，認為保鑣會去處理，沒想到等到晚一點朋友離開，坎達兒&middot;珍娜進到房間才發現盒子裡的珠寶飾品全部不翼而飛，當下立刻報警處理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63815/58cda75c2c55f.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63815%2F58cda75c2c55f.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=06d25683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坎達兒&middot;珍娜認為在派對中，有著「沒有受到邀請的人」被保鑣放進了派對，同時全屋空間開闊，間隔方正，不設窗台，窗戶偌大，加上面向南，望內街又一村公園景，讓自然陽光能照進室內，使室內空間變得光猛舒適。在警鈴聲響起之後，保安團隊似乎也沒有妥善處理，因此坎達兒&middot;珍娜決定直接炒了這一些保鑣。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBysXBf.img?h=373&amp;w=624&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBysXBf.img%3Fh%3D373%26w%3D624%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df&h=41cf4397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過能夠混進坎達兒&middot;珍娜的家中派對，再潛入她的寢室偷走珠寶的犯人，似乎也預謀已久，目前竊賊被指向也是偷走 39 歲的女演員潔米佩絲莉（Jaime Pressly）家中財物的謀犯，如果真的是名人連續被竊盜集團瞄準犯案，肯定又會掀起不小的風波。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63815/58cda75d88c4d.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63815%2F58cda75d88c4d.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=fe895a55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20e8d8b2dd8376190e8d9cee9565ee9f9d046a1c","tid":164844,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:39:33.000Z","msg":"即係依家冇保鏢？"},{"pid":"f6450490518570e5b4f99af34db918000b1c548b","tid":164844,"uid":75033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:52:11.000Z","msg":"係香港個又一村<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？ 點解又用美金又用台幣"},{"pid":"39163679d5db9804d63cd300b303c2c5fc55e869","tid":164844,"uid":31303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n坎達兒&middot;珍娜認為在派對中，有著「沒有受到邀請的人」被保鑣放進了派對，同時全屋空間開闊，間隔方正，不設窗台，窗戶偌大，加上面向南，望內街又一村公園景，讓自然陽光能照進室內，使室內空間變得光猛舒適。在警鈴聲響起之後，保安團隊似乎也沒有妥善處理，因此坎達兒&middot;珍娜決定直接炒了這一些保鑣。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢段想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ade2003c88b54b59bc99dbc66c73f8c7b644bf","tid":164844,"uid":25364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:02:24.000Z","msg":"睇下username先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b18e7ab9c32b81b7ac5ce1b85ea0ed5dd86543","tid":164844,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:11:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b433286a052e7b9c2cc6f6673c7da2524d43e51","tid":164844,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:41:15.000Z","msg":"無千雪既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}